prod.desciption:
The Air Jordan 4 Retro White Oreo features a white leather and mesh upper with hits of Tech Grey on its eyelets and midsole. From there, a red Jumpman logo is embroidered on the tongue, adding a pop of color to the neutral-toned design.

The Air Jordan 4 Retro White Oreo released on Saturday, July 3rd and retailed for $190.
